#: ../../source/janim/items/geometry/line.rst:2
msgid "line"
msgstr "line"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Cmpt_VPoints_LineImpl:1 of
msgid "在线段中，对 :class:`~.Cmpt_VPoints` 的进一步实现"
msgstr "Further implementation of :class:`~.Cmpt_VPoints` in line segments"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Cmpt_VPoints_LineImpl.put_start_and_end_on:1 of
msgid "通过旋转和缩放，使得物件的起点和终点被置于 ``start`` 和 ``end``"
msgstr "Through rotation and scaling, place the item's start and end points at ``start`` and ``end``"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Cmpt_VPoints_LineImpl.get_projection:1 of
msgid "Return projection of a point onto the line"
msgstr "Return projection of a point onto the line"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line:1 of
msgid "线段"
msgstr "Line segment"

#: ../../source/janim/items/geometry/line.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr "Parameters"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line:3 of
msgid "线段起点，可为坐标向量或 :class:`~.Points` 对象；默认为 ``LEFT``"
msgstr "Line start point, can be a coordinate vector or a :class:`~.Points` object; default is ``LEFT``"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line:4 of
msgid "线段终点，可为坐标向量或 :class:`~.Points` 对象；默认为 ``RIGHT``"
msgstr "Line end point, can be a coordinate vector or a :class:`~.Points` object; default is ``RIGHT``"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line:5 janim.items.geometry.line.Line.build_points:7 of
msgid "线段两端的空余量，可为单个数值或者一个元组表示两端的空余量；可用负值表示向外延伸"
msgstr ""
"Buffer at both ends of the line segment; can be a single value or a tuple for both ends. Negative values indicate "
"outward extension"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line:6 of
msgid "线段的弯曲弧度，默认为 ``0``；``0`` 表示直线，非零则是一段圆弧"
msgstr "Curvature angle of the line segment, default is ``0``; ``0`` means a straight line, non-zero means an arc"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line:7 of
msgid "其它参数"
msgstr "Other parameters"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line.reshape:1 of
msgid "类似传递给 ``__init__`` 的参数，重新设置几何物件的形状"
msgstr "Similar to passing parameters to ``__init__``, reset the shape of the geometry item"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line.reshape:3 of
msgid "可以缺省部分值，表示使用先前的；具体用法请参考 :ref:`geometry_reshape` 文档教程"
msgstr ""
"Some values can be omitted to reuse previous ones; for detailed usage, refer to the :ref:`geometry_reshape` tutorial"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line.build_points:1 of
msgid "构建线段的点数据"
msgstr "Build point data for the line segment"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line.build_points:3 of
msgid "基于起点、终点、两端空余量和弯曲弧度生成线段的点数组"
msgstr "Generate the line segment point array from start/end points, end margins, and curvature"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line.build_points:5 of
msgid "线段的起点坐标"
msgstr "Start-point coordinate of the line segment"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line.build_points:6 of
msgid "线段的终点坐标"
msgstr "End-point coordinate of the line segment"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line.build_points:8 of
msgid "线段的弯曲弧度；0 即为直线，非零则是一段圆弧"
msgstr "Curvature angle of the line segment; 0 means a straight line, non-zero means an arc"

#: ../../source/janim/items/geometry/line.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr "Returns"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line.build_points:9 of
msgid "线段的点数据数组"
msgstr "Point-data array of the line segment"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line.pointify_start_and_end:1 of
msgid "将起点与终点输入解析为用于构造线段的三维坐标对"
msgstr "Parse start/end inputs into a pair of 3D coordinates for constructing a line segment"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line.pointify_start_and_end:3 of
msgid "先基于两者的粗略位置计算方向向量，再在输入为边界框时沿该方向提取边界点，从而得到更符合连接方向的首尾点"
msgstr ""
"First compute a direction vector from their rough positions, then if the inputs are bounding boxes, extract boundary "
"points along that direction to get endpoints that better match the connection direction"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line.pointify_start_and_end:5 of
msgid "起点，可为边界框对象或坐标"
msgstr "Start point, can be a bounding-box object or coordinates"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line.pointify_start_and_end:6 of
msgid "终点，可为边界框对象或坐标"
msgstr "End point, can be a bounding-box object or coordinates"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line.pointify_start_and_end:7 of
msgid "解析后的 ``(start, end)`` 三维坐标"
msgstr "Parsed ``(start, end)`` 3D coordinates"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line.pointify:1 of
msgid "将输入解析为三维坐标点"
msgstr "Parse input into a 3D coordinate point"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line.pointify:3 of
msgid "若传入为边界框对象，未给定方向时返回中心点，给定方向时返回该方向上的边界点；若传入坐标序列，则补齐到 3 维后返回"
msgstr ""
"If a bounding-box object is passed, return its center when no direction is given, or return the boundary point in that "
"direction when a direction is given; if a coordinate sequence is passed, pad it to 3D and return"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line.pointify:5 of
msgid "边界框对象或坐标"
msgstr "Bounding-box object or coordinates"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line.pointify:6 of
msgid ""
"用于提取物件坐标，默认为 ``None`` 提取其中心点，或是指定一个方向提取其边界框上指定方向的点（使"
"用 :meth:`~.BoundingBox.get_continuous` ）"
msgstr ""
"Used to extract item coordinates. Default ``None`` extracts the center point; or specify a direction to extract the point "
"on the bounding box in that direction (using :meth:`~.BoundingBox.get_continuous`)"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Line.pointify:7 of
msgid "解析得到的三维坐标"
msgstr "Parsed 3D coordinates"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Cmpt_VPoints_DashedLineImpl:1 of
msgid "在虚线中，对 :class:`~.Cmpt_VPoints` 的进一步实现"
msgstr "Further implementation of :class:`~.Cmpt_VPoints` in dashed lines"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Cmpt_VPoints_DashedLineImpl.get_start:1 of
msgid "得到 ``points`` 的第一个点"
msgstr "Get the first point of ``points``"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Cmpt_VPoints_DashedLineImpl.get_end:1 of
msgid "得到 ``points`` 的最后一个点"
msgstr "Get the last point of ``points``"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.DashedLine:1 of
msgid "虚线"
msgstr "Dashed line"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.DashedLine:3 of
msgid "每段虚线的长度"
msgstr "Length of each dash segment"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.DashedLine:4 of
msgid "虚线段的占比，默认为 ``0.5``，即虚线段与空白段长度相等，但可能因为虚线段描边存在粗细而导致视觉上空白长度略小"
msgstr ""
"Ratio of dash segments, default is ``0.5``, meaning dash segments and gaps have equal length, but the visual gap length "
"may appear slightly smaller due to stroke size"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.DashedLine:5 of
msgid ""
"虚线段长度是否严格遵从 ``dash_length``，默认为 ``False``  - 当为 ``False`` 时，可能会微调以确保首尾都是完整的虚线段 - 当"
"为 ``True`` 时，不再微调，但是尾部虚线段可能不完整  在静态使用的情境下，使用 ``False`` 会更美观；在动态创建的情境下，使用 "
"``True`` 可以避免频繁抖动"
msgstr ""
"Whether the dash segment length strictly follows ``dash_length``, default is ``False`` - When ``False``, may fine-tune to "
"ensure both ends have complete dash segments - When ``True``, no fine-tuning, but the trailing dash segment may be "
"incomplete. For static use, ``False`` looks better; for dynamic creation, ``True`` avoids frequent jittering"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.DashedLine:5 of
msgid "虚线段长度是否严格遵从 ``dash_length``，默认为 ``False``"
msgstr "Whether the dash segment length strictly follows ``dash_length``, default is ``False``"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.DashedLine:7 of
msgid "当为 ``False`` 时，可能会微调以确保首尾都是完整的虚线段"
msgstr "When ``False``, may fine-tune to ensure both ends have complete dash segments"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.DashedLine:8 of
msgid "当为 ``True`` 时，不再微调，但是尾部虚线段可能不完整"
msgstr "When ``True``, no fine-tuning, but the trailing dash segment may be incomplete"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.DashedLine:10 of
msgid "在静态使用的情境下，使用 ``False`` 会更美观；在动态创建的情境下，使用 ``True`` 可以避免频繁抖动"
msgstr "For static use, ``False`` looks better; for dynamic creation, ``True`` avoids frequent jittering"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.DashedLine:12 of
msgid "其它参数，另见 :class:`Line`"
msgstr "Other parameters, see also :class:`Line`"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.DashedLine:16 of
msgid "由于一些因素，:class:`~.DashedLine` 并不完全具有 :class:`~.Line` 的功能"
msgstr "Due to some reasons, :class:`~.DashedLine` does not fully have all capabilities of :class:`~.Line`"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.DashedLine:18 of
msgid ""
"这是由于 :class:`~.DashedLine` 实际上将每段虚线作为子物件来实现，而去除了自己本身的 ``points`` 数据， 这会导致包括 "
"``.reshape`` 以及 ``.points.vector`` 等一些方法不可用"
msgstr ""
"This is because :class:`~.DashedLine` is implemented by treating each dash segment as a child item and removing its own "
"``points`` data, which makes some methods unavailable, including ``.reshape`` and ``.points.vector``"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.TangentLine:1 of
msgid "切线"
msgstr "Tangent line"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.TangentLine:3 of
msgid "传入 ``vitem`` 表示需要做切线的物件，``alpha`` 表示切点在 ``vitem`` 上的比例"
msgstr ""
"Pass ``vitem`` as the item to create a tangent line for, ``alpha`` represents the proportion of the tangent point on "
"``vitem``"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.TangentLine:4 of
msgid "``length``: 切线长度"
msgstr "``length``: Length of the tangent line"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.TangentLine:5 of
msgid "``d_alpha``: 精细程度，越小越精细（默认 ``1e-6``）"
msgstr "``d_alpha``: Precision level, smaller values mean higher precision (default ``1e-6``)"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Elbow:1 of
msgid "折线（一般用作直角符号），关于直接基于两条线创建的直角符号，另请参见 :class:`~.RightAngle`"
msgstr ""
"Elbow (generally used as a right angle symbol). For right angle symbols created directly from two lines, see "
"also :class:`~.RightAngle`"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Elbow:3 of
msgid "直角标记的边长"
msgstr "Side length of the right angle marker"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Elbow:4 of
msgid "起始角度"
msgstr "Starting angle"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Angle:1 of
msgid "一个圆弧或直角标记对象，用于表示两条线之间的夹角"
msgstr "An arc or right angle marker object used to represent the angle between two lines"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Angle:3 of
msgid "``radius``: 圆弧的半径"
msgstr "``radius``: Radius of the arc"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Angle:5 of
msgid "``quadrant``:"
msgstr "``quadrant``:"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Angle of
msgid "由两个整数构成的序列，用于确定应使用哪一个象限为基准；"
msgstr "A sequence of two integers used to determine which quadrant to use as reference;"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Angle of
msgid "第一个值表示在第一条线上以终点(1)或起点(-1)为基准，第二个值同理作用于第二条线；"
msgstr ""
"The first value indicates using the end point (1) or start point (-1) as reference on the first line, the second value "
"similarly applies to the second line;"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Angle of
msgid "可选值包括： ``(1, 1)``, ``(1, -1)``, ``(-1, 1)``, ``(-1, -1)``"
msgstr "Optional values include: ``(1, 1)``, ``(1, -1)``, ``(-1, 1)``, ``(-1, -1)``"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Angle:10 of
msgid "``other_angle``:"
msgstr "``other_angle``:"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Angle of
msgid "在两个可能的夹角之间切换。默认 ``False``，则弧线从 ``line1`` 到 ``line2`` 按逆时针绘制；"
msgstr ""
"Switch between two possible angles. Default ``False`` means the arc is drawn counterclockwise from ``line1`` to ``line2``;"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Angle of
msgid "如果为 ``True``，则按顺时针方向绘制"
msgstr "If ``True``, draw in clockwise direction"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Angle:14 of
msgid "``dot``: 是否在弧线上添加一个点，通常用于指示直角"
msgstr "``dot``: Whether to add a dot on the arc, usually used to indicate a right angle"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Angle:16 of
msgid "``dot_radius``: 点的半径，默认为弧半径的 ``1/10``"
msgstr "``dot_radius``: Radius of the dot, default is ``1/10`` of the arc radius"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Angle:18 of
msgid "``dot_distance``: 点到圆心的相对距离，其中 ``0`` 表示在圆心处，``1`` 表示在圆弧上，默认为 ``0.55``"
msgstr ""
"``dot_distance``: Relative distance from the dot to the center, where ``0`` means at the center, ``1`` means on the arc, "
"default is ``0.55``"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Angle:20 of
msgid "``dot_color``: 点的颜色"
msgstr "``dot_color``: Color of the dot"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Angle:22 of
msgid "``elbow``: 是否使用直角标记的形式，参考 :class:`RightAngle` 类"
msgstr "``elbow``: Whether to use the right angle marker form, refer to :class:`RightAngle` class"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Angle.get_lines:1 of
msgid "返回一个包含构成该角的两个 :class:`~.Line` 的 :class:`~.Group` 对象"
msgstr "Return a :class:`~.Group` object containing the two :class:`~.Line` objects that form this angle"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Angle.get_value:1 of
msgid "获取该角的数值"
msgstr "Get the numerical value of this angle"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Angle.get_value:3 of
msgid "``degrees``: 是否以角度的形式返回，默认为 ``False``，即弧度制"
msgstr "``degrees``: Whether to return in degrees, default is ``False``, i.e., radians"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.Angle.from_three_points:1 of
msgid "由三点构造一个角，表示 ∠ABC，点 ``B`` 为角的顶点"
msgstr "Construct an angle from three points, representing ∠ABC, where point ``B`` is the vertex"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.RightAngle:1 of
msgid "一个用于表示直角的 :class:`Elbow` 样式的对象（L 形折角）"
msgstr "An object in :class:`Elbow` style (L-shaped corner) used to represent a right angle"

#: janim.items.geometry.line.RightAngle:3 of
msgid "``length``: 直角标记的边长"
msgstr "``length``: Side length of the right angle marker"
